casebody.data:
MOTION DOCKET

95-2582. In re Boatman.

Defiance County, No. 4-95-7. On January 22, 1996, appellee filed a memorandum in response which was due January 17, 1996. S.CtPrac.R. XIV(1)(C) prohibits the *1508filing of documents that are not timely tendered for filing. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, effective January 29,1996, that appellee’s memorandum in response be, and hereby is, stricken.
